## Current State
`runSubagent()` subscribes to session events but only accumulates output, calls `onUpdate` once before/after. User sees nothing until done.

## How to Fix

The `onUpdate` callback can be called **continuously** during execution — each call updates the tool row in real-time:

```typescript
// In runSubagent, pass onUpdate through:
async function runSubagent(specialist, task, cwd, parentCtx, signal, onUpdate) {
  // ...
  const unsubscribe = session.subscribe((event) => {
    // Stream each event to the UI
    onUpdate?.({
      content: [{ type: "text", text: `[${specialist.name}] ${event.type}: ${event.delta || ''}` }],
      details: { specialist: specialist.name, status: "running" },
    });
  });
}
```

