| `orchestrator.ts` | Currently: once before/after |
| `examples/extensions/subagent/index.ts` | Every JSON line from subprocess → live UI |
| `extensions.md` docs | `onUpdate` replaces previous display each call |

## Trade-off
Real-time streaming = more tokens in parent context (each update is a message). Could add an option: `stream: true/false`.

